"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[decision] Revisit Hive-Mind Project Phase 7 Implementation: The user has directed a return to the Hive-Mind project, specifically Phase 7. The previous implementation is deemed incorrect. The directive is to study how Hermes handles OAuth and API key authentication. The goal is to implement a similar authentication flow within Hive-Mind, using Hermes as a reference for its code and login process, but without direct dependency. After successful authentication (via OAuth or API key), the system should display available models for selection. A complete study and implementation plan are requested before proceeding.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"qji6r6","at":1782088666543},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.0633113,-0.00166446,-0.02171778,-0.10890156,-0.05010216,0.07116034,-0.02098355,-0.02234643,0.01557257,-0.01059015,0.05965352,-0.06225327,-0.00164072,0.02181985,0.00369548,0.00417676,0.01526569,0.01282891,0.00360649,0.04219954,0.02143966,-0.03130767,0.03616107,-0.0369487,-0.04329189,0.0412581,-0.0421655,-0.02292846,-0.03628698,-0.19781104,0.03180275,-0.04064512,0.00201377,0.00807363,-0.050937,-0.02640016,0.0046742,0.00749005,-0.04777974,0.02504936,0.02301118,0.0127722,-0.00153432,-0.03224104,-0.03284984,-0.01098528,-0.01119665,0.01700318,-0.05045367,-0.06927007,-0.02341788,0.0509487,-0.00699512,0.03539473,0.04138111,0.05625256,0.01418448,0.06359825,0.01093203,0.06059586,0.05035111,-0.00412411,-0.18507563,0.07479756,0.06262796,0.04984984,-0.04610807,-0.07525853,0.00813622,0.0493379,-0.06609788,-0.00069634,-0.00269699,0.04023381,0.06839782,0.03445588,-0.05868006,-0.02244709,0.04041395,-0.04338372,-0.06179,0.01666923,0.00415373,0.00085805,-0.01265811,0.01548234,-0.00759534,-0.01967433,-0.00549718,-0.02224975,-0.01149343,-0.01700839,-0.03900411,-0.02165345,0.01619451,0.01801827,0.02750988,0.02852735,-0.07200749,0.12884462,-0.02963792,0.03249714,-0.0385050