"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[bugfix] ComfyUI: Fix NotImplementedError for Float8_e4m3fn in CUDA operations: The user encountered a `NotImplementedError` in ComfyUI when attempting to use the SamplerCustomAdvanced node. The error message, `\"mul_cuda\" not implemented for 'Float8_e4m3fn'`, indicates that a specific CUDA operation required for multiplication is not supported for the `Float8_e4m3fn` data type. This prevented the sampler from executing correctly. The error originates within the custom sampler nodes, specifically during the `sample` method call which eventually leads to a CUDA operation that lacks support for this particular floating-point format.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"9p17h","at":1782088666607},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00877008,-0.01268475,0.0267639,-0.04337576,0.00261916,-0.00621258,-0.07841208,-0.00635791,0.00504929,-0.02217848,0.01986525,-0.05699377,0.01051841,0.0352526,0.02012286,0.06673495,-0.04329757,0.02800023,0.04341691,0.05077663,0.07030229,0.00680551,0.01272307,-0.02032926,0.01761878,0.05069592,-0.0218493,-0.09797531,-0.0545097,-0.2784608,0.00518363,0.00172254,0.05870938,-0.04098151,0.04400528,-0.0716047,-0.03507682,0.00168406,0.05204749,0.05670479,-0.02470783,0.04046346,-0.04639644,-0.02178651,0.03025071,-0.00642772,-0.0399438,-0.00793804,0.06133774,-0.04022732,-0.03440233,-0.01905373,-0.01960289,0.01116139,0.00107618,0.07108139,0.00061618,-0.02795289,0.03331374,0.06282052,0.06188849,0.03140764,-0.18453258,0.05117242,0.04949948,-0.00999225,0.03873779,-0.04663953,0.06488984,0.05588967,-0.05250083,-0.01461105,0.01249815,0.03682747,-0.01007846,0.00866272,-0.0010149,-0.03542996,-0.01095179,-0.02032985,0.01359485,0.00161863,-0.00928407,0.0019247,0.03328381,-0.04090775,-0.00998095,0.00361787,0.04752737,0.02808881,-0.02083908,-0.00600375,-0.04698785,0.06248093,-0.03456727,0.0066768,0.0757392,0.02943531,-0.10579129,0.09550347,-0.01271967,-0.01