"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[discovery] Project Architecture: Cortex Regulatory Assistant: The project \"Cortex\" is a specialized regulatory assistant designed to analyze documents from the São Paulo state gas regulatory agency (ARSESP). It implements a sophisticated RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) pipeline that transforms raw documents from SharePoint into curated chunks for vector search. The infrastructure is tightly integrated with Databricks, utilizing Databricks Asset Bundles for deployment across dev, staging, and production environments.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1ss4ldz","at":1782088666677},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05817052,0.03664174,0.02362425,-0.05686755,-0.00964515,-0.00203714,0.01753526,-0.01100162,0.02359837,0.0145836,0.03659377,-0.0708643,0.03805415,0.04339719,0.03165323,0.01211639,-0.03025144,0.01188208,0.10574368,0.01418521,0.04786297,-0.0310018,-0.01896397,0.00446238,-0.02811858,0.08089098,-0.05329467,-0.07408916,-0.06637651,-0.22215486,0.06584035,0.01449814,0.06546532,-0.03199492,-0.01917852,-0.01198859,-0.04591212,0.05383414,-0.02417643,0.04895644,0.03438487,-0.04046266,-0.03296307,-0.01655929,-0.04461572,-0.01632587,-0.01076264,-0.04414164,-0.03205489,-0.03476255,0.01949466,-0.02800819,0.01345297,0.01920695,0.01709337,0.03834347,0.02809495,0.03164802,0.03416581,0.05587298,0.05680716,0.04169237,-0.20639956,0.08218101,0.0587105,0.03139799,-0.08087726,-0.04494609,0.05044303,0.02298651,-0.00517984,0.00170267,0.02080972,0.0116565,0.07901347,0.04083787,0.01485846,-0.03969463,-0.00632636,-0.0541425,-0.01273218,0.01422188,-0.01649079,0.00768111,0.00632053,-0.00273757,-0.01416946,0.03251637,0.04338283,0.09762122,-0.05167237,0.00020433,-0.01049988,0.04064794,-0.07097698,-0.08133791,-0.00219905,0.00386166,-0.02497743,0.14678647,-0.05715644,0.00964099,0.03423014,-0.05819688,-0.01683383,-0.03541889,0.06094848,-0.02416559,-0.0358986,-0.04400957,-0.0