"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[refactor] Revisit Hive-Mind Phase 7 Implementation: The user has identified an issue with the current implementation of Phase 7 for the Hive-Mind project. Specifically, the authentication and API key handling, which was intended to be modeled after the Hermes system, was not done correctly. The directive is to conduct a thorough study of how Hermes manages OAuth and API key authentication and then implement a similar, but independent, mechanism for Hive. This new implementation should allow users to log in using either OAuth or an API key, and subsequently display available models for selection.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"zltrk1","at":1782088666784},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06581714,-0.00257658,-0.00685765,-0.10875766,-0.02922405,0.05879568,-0.0170849,-0.02443716,0.01637159,-0.01385119,0.06334493,-0.06935955,-0.00107023,0.01689177,-0.00170401,-0.01125228,0.00914449,0.01190478,0.01595556,0.02826329,0.02138008,-0.01721859,0.03792221,-0.03314576,-0.06717908,0.06094906,-0.0450527,-0.02274943,-0.02736357,-0.2136745,0.02581775,-0.04221605,0.01561615,0.00597885,-0.04358838,-0.0331091,0.00533695,0.00237621,-0.03976801,0.01588949,0.02293176,0.00857004,-0.02458467,-0.0234249,-0.03906135,-0.01141242,-0.00063965,0.01685496,-0.05242289,-0.06766877,-0.02126569,0.03942867,-0.00389688,0.00926434,0.03565914,0.04391299,0.02296277,0.04400663,0.00181458,0.06828325,0.07561721,-0.01708571,-0.18174052,0.0847534,0.06553852,0.04747766,-0.04023758,-0.07038183,0.00741564,0.04218704,-0.06276334,0.0126845,-0.00302722,0.04846162,0.05896789,0.00851843,-0.0517268,-0.0176612,0.02202411,-0.04268592,-0.06797528,0.01937783,-0.00031082,0.00549175,-0.02343933,0.01505965,-0.00568925,-0.01860903,-0.00323542,-0.03837128,-0.02318321,-0.00464378,-0.02448112,-0.00634876,0.02485374,0.02143508,0.01330655,0.03096522,-0.07060929,0.12761782,-0.02192738,0.0243164,-0.03094883,-0.078602