"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[decision] Re-evaluate Hive-Mind Phase 7 Implementation: The user has identified a critical flaw in the Phase 7 implementation of the Hive-Mind project. The previous attempt failed to correctly integrate authentication mechanisms, specifically regarding OAuth and API key handling. The user's directive is to perform a thorough study of how the 'Hermes' system manages these authentication methods. This study should inform a new implementation for Hive-Mind that mirrors Hermes' approach to logging in via OAuth or API key, and subsequently presents available models for selection. A comprehensive plan for this re-implementation is required before proceeding.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"12903bf","at":1782088666970},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06415443,-0.0068635,0.00251069,-0.09999372,-0.04120772,0.06188669,0.00737503,-0.01377676,0.01166232,-0.01158593,0.0488317,-0.05765971,0.00012514,0.02660378,0.01964358,-0.00555705,0.00799796,0.02010062,0.02965684,0.04124568,0.02067056,-0.00733529,0.02508528,-0.0367098,-0.05850755,0.04531228,-0.04418117,-0.03236373,-0.03299629,-0.2158889,0.02629118,-0.03833678,0.00709971,0.00025916,-0.03226635,-0.04804461,-0.00914769,0.00454745,-0.01490205,0.00370961,0.0116564,0.00183562,-0.03258105,-0.03137054,-0.03452683,-0.00839959,-0.00406813,0.0169869,-0.05586968,-0.07179317,-0.03136561,0.05279478,0.00930549,0.03210796,0.03513984,0.0403667,0.03107427,0.0710943,0.00611554,0.06823403,0.06700111,-0.00067636,-0.18324116,0.07799404,0.07381188,0.03785976,-0.04061452,-0.07260294,0.0030582,0.03975346,-0.06267216,0.00029064,-0.00003,0.03295761,0.05071646,0.04411418,-0.05195841,-0.02881863,0.02434865,-0.03999916,-0.04644586,0.02559793,0.00897717,-0.00556099,-0.03203658,0.01691935,-0.01002511,-0.01758668,-0.00458093,-0.03218843,-0.00103378,0.00301253,-0.01302316,-0.01840643,0.02360392,0.01553105,0.0153078,0.02653305,-0.09083645,0.11