"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[bugfix] LanceDB Embedding Failure Resolution: The \"Invalid range 0..0\" error in LanceDB was diagnosed as a failure to handle empty files and a performance bottleneck caused by large binary assets. To resolve this, a `.kilocodeignore` file was implemented to exclude these problematic files from the indexing process. This ensures the embedding pipeline can complete without crashing. The fix was documented across the delivery log, project memory, and traceability matrix to ensure long-term maintainability.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"q90qyh","at":1782088667035},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06151728,-0.04217498,0.04589772,-0.05027367,-0.00800552,-0.01695757,-0.10473514,-0.03649676,-0.00753611,0.06196804,0.05059228,-0.07911094,0.07881882,0.03812389,-0.01488487,0.02290867,-0.01115176,0.01653212,0.04306165,0.06498931,0.04662806,-0.00466242,0.01565027,0.00062925,-0.00723596,0.15283033,-0.0322976,-0.09942126,-0.08040335,-0.27576059,-0.00295261,-0.03555468,0.06579978,0.02717261,0.0194599,-0.05357549,-0.03420403,0.03092374,-0.02526072,0.02327618,-0.00567461,0.01591734,-0.02357788,-0.04115159,-0.02017888,-0.07130769,-0.02836922,-0.00833236,0.06436467,-0.04043759,-0.08295192,-0.03524169,-0.01847101,-0.02086557,0.01423983,0.050391,0.02246015,0.05810927,0.03749046,0.05728101,0.03920044,-0.00946488,-0.15669291,0.05127968,0.05964676,0.03574234,-0.02211845,-0.01740933,0.01659217,0.04088665,-0.05574138,-0.05971371,0.01744751,0.08538114,-0.00137506,0.00053798,0.04536909,0.02706999,-0.00296648,-0.01857078,0.01476733,-0.01800107,0.01599815,-0.03816275,-0.00783109,-0.07057363,0.01415518,0.01171676,0.03042567,0.0300593,0.02880337,0.01338607,0.03789464,0.01313519,-0.0657116,-0.05297023,0.03376057,0.00028639,-0.06468762,0.12760115,-0.02251297,-0.02037198,0.0110037,0.00713606,0.03671376,-0.01891658,0.02723656,-0.02541833,-0.02308704,-0.03622461,-0.01032739,-0.07431