"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1442-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 14:42#[decision] Re-evaluation of Hive-Mind Phase 7 Implementation: The user has directed a significant re-evaluation of the ongoing Hive-Mind project, specifically Phase 7. The current implementation is deemed incorrect. The primary directive is to thoroughly investigate and understand the authentication mechanisms (OAuth and API key handling) employed by a system referred to as \"Hermes.\" The objective is to extract the principles and patterns from Hermes' approach and apply them to the Hive-Mind project. This includes replicating the login flow using OAuth or API keys and subsequently enabling the selection of models. Before any new implementation begins, a comprehensive study and a detailed implementation plan are mandated.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1q0sj31","at":1782088667192},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07321102,-0.01621274,0.00442891,-0.09613782,-0.01898696,0.07801007,-0.01345846,-0.0094219,0.01280388,-0.01849669,0.05619353,-0.05863898,0.01063036,0.01677499,0.00945867,-0.00261719,0.01453773,0.00021754,0.02188784,0.0265871,0.03152921,-0.01501711,0.03779012,-0.02199201,-0.02828869,0.05151461,-0.04490647,-0.01541914,-0.03679849,-0.21545516,0.02799246,-0.0348631,0.0085968,0.00227947,-0.03213448,-0.04313022,-0.0082317,0.00691283,-0.02572443,0.00974431,0.02007235,0.01119323,-0.02619142,-0.01424941,-0.04776357,0.00585557,-0.01465954,0.00140801,-0.06996544,-0.06120404,-0.02874792,0.02559916,0.0035947,0.02135649,0.03624854,0.05350091,0.02438509,0.05070981,0.01850418,0.07956532,0.06639569,-0.00237354,-0.1965826,0.08004717,0.06790853,0.03462211,-0.04144878,-0.06880423,0.00459424,0.03256979,-0.0758266,-0.01006716,0.00484607,0.04172195,0.05900513,0.04352575,-0.04818899,-0.02015105,0.02169668,-0.03650844,-0.03997011,0.03294539,0.01660589,-0.00820425,-0.00899232,0.00973414,-0.00010413,-0.00429642,0.00189654,-0.02528281,-0.00357249,0.00416913,-0.019415